message.body: Should we come now or wait until later because of traffic?
Traffic doesn't look too bad right now. I can head out anytime.
I'm still an hour and a half away.
Yes... Or so google says. They say Poolesville. But same thing.
Ok. GPS says 4:30. But I bet it will be later with traffic.
Yeah, traffic will pick up soon, at least going away from DC. On my route out there for sure. I'll expect longer for both of us.
